Class GenericVector<E>

java.lang.Object
org.jscience.mathematics.linearalgebra.vectors.GenericVector<E>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Vector<E>, AbelianGroup<Vector<E>>, AbelianMonoid<Vector<E>>, Group<Vector<E>>, Magma<Vector<E>>, Monoid<Vector<E>>, Set<Vector<E>>, Module<Vector<E>, E>
Direct Known Subclasses:
DenseVector, SparseVector
public class GenericVector<E> extends Object implements Vector<E>
A generic vector implementation using abstract storage and provider delegation.
Since:
1.0
Author:
Silvere Martin-Michiellot, Gemini AI (Google DeepMind)
